snippet.title: Promenade - Official Reveal Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description: Embark on an adventure through a colorful world in Promenade, and watch the trailer to see what to expect from this upcoming game, coming to PC and consoles in 2023.
